dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Spellman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The change\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris Olympics 2024 However, there was another shocking twist in the tale as the Court of Arbitration for Sport ruled that the judging panel had made an error in improving Chiles' score given the appeal was issued outside of the one-minute window set by the International Gymnastics Federation.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Gymnastics Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 658}, {\"ngram\": \"another shocking twist\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"the tale\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"the Court\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"Arbitration\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"the judging panel\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles' score\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the appeal\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It meant Chiles was pushed back to fifth spot, while Barbosu returned to the medal places - a decision which has left USA gymnastics 'devastated'.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"fifth spot\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"Barbosu\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal places\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"USA gymnastics\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am taking this time and removing myself from social media for my mental health.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you,' Chiles later told her followers on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.118051388955161e-27, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"her followers\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Chiles has since remained tight-lipped regarding the controversial ruling, her sister has been anything but - blasting the decision and urging fans to have her sibling in their prayers.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversial ruling\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"her sister\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"their prayers\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Please keep Jordan (and my family) in your prayers.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7957190220078302, \"rank\": 0.17916341499077254, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"your prayers\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Racism is real, it exists, it is alive and well,' she wrote on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.118051388955161e-27, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Racism\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They have officially, 5 days later, stripped her of one of her medals.\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her medals\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not because she did not win, not because she was drugged, not because she stepped out of bounds.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bounds\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not because she wasn't good enough.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But because the judges failed to give her difficulty and forced an inquiry to be made.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"her difficulty\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"an inquiry\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'FOUR SECONDS.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"'FOUR SECONDS\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her bronze was stripped over 4 seconds of time that would have never needed to happen if the judges did their job.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her bronze\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"over 4 seconds\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"their job\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I love you baby sis.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I got yo back no matter what.'\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"yo\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: 'Just so yall aware - in the HISTORY of the Olympics NO ONE has ever been stripped of their medal for this.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the HISTORY\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"NO ONE\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"their medal\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Also - there are only TWO ways you can be stripped of a medal.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only TWO ways\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheating or doping.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doping\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She did neither.'\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"neither\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a later post, Jazmin stressed that she did not think racism was the 'root cause' of her sister's medal being removed.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a later post\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"Jazmin\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"racism\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2323}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'root cause\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"her sister's medal\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And just to make sumn [sic] clear - the racism that's BEHIND the comments and vulgar and vile comments that are being made toward my sister is what I am speaking on,' she continued.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sumn\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2405}, {\"ngram\": \"clear - the racism\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"the comments\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"vulgar and vile comments\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"my sister\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am not calling them young ladies racist not am I saying racism is the root cause of this.\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"young ladies\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"racism\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"the root cause\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am saying it's alive and well because in the last 5 days she has been called blacky.\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last 5 days\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A monkey.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A monkey\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ni***r. And much more!!\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ni***r\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2765}]}, {\"sentence\"